Monitoring Stack (Prometheus + Grafana + Blackbox + Node Exporter + cAdvisor + Loki + Promtail) using Docker Compose

Overview:

This project creates a full monitoring + logging stack on an EC2 Ubuntu server using Docker Compose.
What you will get"

1.Prometheus: collects metrics (monitoring data)
2.Grafana: dashboards and visualization
3.Blackbox Exporter: monitors website uptime (HTTP/HTTPS) and DNS (optional)
4.Node Exporter: server metrics (CPU/RAM/Disk/Network)
5.cAdvisor: Docker container metrics (CPU/RAM/Network per container)
6.Loki: log database (stores logs)
7.Promtail: log shipper (reads logs from server/docker and pushes to Loki)


